  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this research is to help understand the relative importance of changes in&#xD;
      insulin secretion (which lowers glucose) and changes in glucagon (which raises glucose) to&#xD;
      regulate metabolism and the body's ability to make glucose.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
